The goal of this project is to develop diagnostics and prognostics schemes by using a model of the physical system.  The output of the model and the physical system are compared and a residual is generated.  The residual is conpared with that of a predefined threshold and a fault is declared when the residual exceeds the threshold. Based on this effort, a tool set has been developed in LabVIEW.

